# ============================
# AI / Agent Tooling (2026+)
# ============================
# These files are primarily for local AI coding agent workflows.
# They change frequently and have limited long-term value to human contributors.
# Only commit them if you have a strong, ongoing reason.

AGENTS.md
.cursor/
.agents/

# Agent configuration and generated artifacts
docs/prds/
docs/ai/

# AI session decision logs (use docs/decisions/ for real ADRs instead)
docs/*-decisions.md
docs/*decisions.md

